videos.headline: Aces catch fire with 19-2 run to start to Game 2
videos.description: The Las Vegas Aces pick up where they left off in Game 1 with a 19-2 run in the first quarter against the Liberty.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Aces catch fire with 19-2 run to start to Game 2) 2023/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jonquel Jones fights through a double-team for an and-1 bucket
videos.description: Jonquel Jones converts a 3-point play as the Liberty cut into the Aces' advantage.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Jonquel Jones fights through a double team for an and-1 bucket) 2023/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aces ball movement leads to buzzer-beating 3 from Chelsea Gray
videos.description: Chelsea Gray gets the 3-point shot off just before the buzzer to extend the Aces' lead over the Liberty.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Aces ball movement leads to buzzer-beating 3 from Chelsea Gray) 2023/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chelsea Gray caps historic 1st quarter with buzzer-beater
videos.description: Chelsea Gray drills a jumper to give the Aces a WNBA Finals-record 38 points in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Chelsea Gray caps historic 1st quarter with buzzer-beater) 2023/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kelsey Plum somehow hits the acrobatic and-1 basket
videos.description: Kelsey Plum with one of the day's best plays!, 10/11/2023

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Kelsey Plum with one of the day's best plays!) 2023/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Liberty use 12-0 run to get back into game
videos.description: The Liberty respond in the second quarter with a run of their own to cut into the Aces' lead.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Liberty use 12-0 run to get back into game) 2023/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kelsey Plum crosses up Stefanie Dolson and drills a 3
videos.description: Kelsey Plum drains a deep 3-pointer after shaking Stefanie Dolson with some nice handles.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (What a shot by Kelsey Plum) 2023/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: A'ja Wilson: Aces 'took care of home court'
videos.description: A'ja Wilson reflects on the Aces' big Game 2 win over the Liberty.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (A'ja Wilson: Aces 'took care of home court') 2023/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aces dominate Liberty to take 2-0 lead in WNBA Finals
videos.description: Three Aces surpass 20 points on the night as Las Vegas beats New York 104-76 in Game 2 of the WNBA Finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Highlight (Aces dominate Liberty to take 2-0 lead in WNBA Finals) 2023/10/11 ESHEET SC
